scene.message:
Nanjo: Truth is stranger{nl}
than fiction...{nl}
How well that's said.{waitkey}{ret}

{color:3}Maki's Mother.{nl}
Works at SEBEC.{nl}
An elite engineer.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: H-hey!{nl}
We almost forgot{nl}
about Maki's mom!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: This wound...{nl}
it's from a bullet.{nl}
Who did this to you?{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mother: Everything{nl}
wrong with this city...{nl}
it's all Kandori's doing...{waitkey}{nl}
I was involved as an{nl}
engineer in the development{nl}
of a certain device.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: A device...{nl}
Are you saying that machine{nl}
caused all of this?{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mother:{nl}
The Deva System...{nl}
It artificially alters{nl}
space itself...{waitkey}{clearbox}That it would lead to{nl}
results like this...{nl}
Kandori said he didn't{nl}
care what happened here.{waitkey}{nl}
We have to warn{nl}
the police, fast...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: I'm afraid that{nl}
won't work...{nl}
The police station is{nl}
already full of demons.{waitkey}{nl}
I just saw it{nl}
myself.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mother: Good heavens...{nl}
Someone has to{nl}
stop Kandori...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: ...Ma'am,{nl}
how did you{nl}
get away?{waitkey}{ret}

Maki's Mother: The abandoned{nl}
factory has a secret{nl}
loading entrance...{nl}
With this Security Card...{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Ma'am!{nl}
...Thank goodness —{nl}
she just fainted.{nl}
We need to move!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: ...{ctl0f:1}{nl}
Leaving the rest{nl}
to you guys.{nl}
Gonna go settle this.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Wait, Inaba.{nl}
Nothing ventured,{nl}
nothing gained.{nl}
I'll come too.{waitkey}{nl}
Besides, without{nl}
that card, we can't{nl}
get near Kandori.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: W-wait a second!...{wait_fr:88}{nl}
Fine, whatever!{nl}
We'll get back to{nl}
school on our own!{waitkey}{clearbox}Honestly, men!{nl}
They never stop to{nl}
think how it feels{nl}
to be left behind.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: They really are alike,{nl}
those two — so reckless.{waitkey}{nl}
Well, once they see{nl}
how it goes, they'll{nl}
give up and come back.{waitkey}{ret}

Butterfly: If you are hurt{nl}
before you reach the school,{nl}
return to me.{nl}
I shall give you strength...{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Still...{nl}
What on earth is{nl}
this butterfly?{waitkey}{clearbox}Thinking about it{nl}
won't help, I guess...{nl}
Let's just get back{nl}
to school fast.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: What a mysterious{nl}
butterfly...{nl}
Don't you feel like it can{nl}
see into your very heart?{waitkey}{ret}

Butterfly: Young ones{nl}
who are wounded...{nl}
Close your eyes...{waitkey}{ret}
